title: The Fog is Lifting (DVDR) Must See!
description:
Unreliable sources have made Islam by far the most misunderstood religion in the world. 

The Fog is Lifting is a series of documentaries that challenges your knowledge about the Islamic faith and traditions. 

In this DVD titled Islam in Brief - the first part of The Fog is Lifting- 
you will learn in 74 minutes more information than what you can acquire in 74 days of reading. 

The official website of the documentary: http://www.fogislifting.com
